"title": "9023: death, of unbelievers",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "9023",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The departure from the present life of unrepentant people to await final banishment from God.</p>\n<h2>Death is inevitable</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps49:10\">PSA 49:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:48\">PSA 89:48</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam14:14\">2SA 14:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job30:23\">JOB 30:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:36\">PSA 37:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl3:19-Eccl3:20\">ECC 3:19–3:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl8:8\">ECC 8:8</a></p>\n<h2>The premature death of unbelievers is the consequence of sin</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:27\">PRO 10:27</a></strong> <em>OT writers, for whom God's blessing on the righteous occurs mostly in the present life, often saw early or sudden death as divine judgment on the wicked.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr10:13\">1CH 10:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job22:16\">JOB 22:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:17\">PSA 9:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:1-Ps37:2\">PSA 37:1–37:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:22\">PSA 37:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps37:38\">PSA 37:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps55:23\">PSA 55:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps139:19\">PSA 139:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov5:21-Prov5:23\">PRO 5:21–5:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:19\">PRO 11:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:12\">PRO 14:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa17:14\">ISA 17:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek3:19\">EZK 3:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek18:4\">EZK 18:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek18:20\">EZK 18:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:30\">DAN 5:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:20\">LUK 12:20</a></p>\n<h2>Aspects of the death of unbelievers</h2>\n<h3>They die unforgiven</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:21\">JHN 8:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:24\">JHN 8:24</a></p>\n<h3>They die without hope</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:7\">PRO 11:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl8:10\">ECC 8:10</a></p>\n<h3>God has no pleasure in their death</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek18:23\">EZK 18:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek18:32\">EZK 18:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:9\">2PE 3:9</a></p>\n<h2>Descriptions of the death of unbelievers</h2>\n<h3>Being destroyed</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:13\">MAT 7:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:22\">ROM 9:22</a></p>\n<h3>Perishing</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:16\">JHN 3:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:12\">2PE 2:12</a></p>\n<h3>Being in fire</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:22-Luke16:24\">LUK 16:22–16:24</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:27\">HEB 10:27</a></p>\n<h3>Being in darkness</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:30\">MAT 25:30</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:17\">2PE 2:17</a></p>\n<h2>The consequences of the death of unbelievers</h2>\n<h3>The intermediate state of awaiting judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:13\">REV 20:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:23\">LUK 16:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:29\">JHN 5:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts24:15\">ACT 24:15</a></p>\n<h3>The judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:27\">HEB 9:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:29\">JHN 5:29</a></p>\n<h3>The eternal consequences</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan12:2\">DAN 12:2</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:41\">MAT 25:41</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:8\">MAT 18:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:46\">MAT 25:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:45-Mark9:48\">MRK 9:45–9:48</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:8-Gal1:9\">GAL 1:8–1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:2\">HEB 6:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:7\">JUD 1:7</a></p>\n<h2>The challenge of the death of unbelievers</h2>\n<h3>The call to prepare</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:1\">2KI 20:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl7:17\">ECC 7:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl9:10\">ECC 9:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos4:12\">AMO 4:12</a></p>\n<h3>The only escape is through Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:51\">JHN 8:51</a></strong> <em>Death for believers is swallowed up in life, so that they are never personally aware of the pain and sting of death (compare <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:26\">Jn 11:26</a>).</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:24\">JHN 5:24</a></p>",
